overviewContent: I am a programming student at Cégep de l'Abitibi-Témiscamingue and at Laval University in Québec in Computer Science. I am passionate about developing innovative and efficient solutions. My education has provided me with strong skills in computer science and programming, which I apply to various projects. Constantly seeking new knowledge, I strive to enhance my technical skills and contribute meaningfully to every project I work on.
